from dzk danny keren subject re desertification of the negev thi be nonsense i live in the negev for many year and i can say for sure that no beduin be move or harm in any way on the contrary their standard of live ha climb sharply many of them now live in rather nice permanent house and own car there be quite a few beduin student in the ben-gurion university there be good friendly relation between them and the rest of the population all the beduin i meet would be rather surprise to read mr davidson poster i have to say danny keren 